ng into it directly.   Try the following command sequences." }}{PARA 
0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 6 "p1(
x);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#,&*$)-%\"xG6#F'\"\"#\"\"\"F*F*!
