w you specified the variable to be x in p2 and then set the equation t
o zero and solved the factors." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 
1 0 12 "solve(p1=0);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6$\"\"\"!\"\"" }
}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 82 "you set the expression equal to \+
