riable to solve for, for example when we included ,b it solved b in te
rms of the other variables" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 
"" 0 "" {TEXT -1 107 "Use the solve command replacing x with a, b, c r
