lve(p3=0,a);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#,$*&,&*&%\"bG\"\"\"%\"
xGF(F(%\"cGF(F(F)!\"#!\"\"" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 61 "set
s the equation equal to zero and solves for the variable a" }}}{EXCHG 
