{XPPMATH 20 "6#,$*&,&*&%\"aG\"\"\")%\"xG\"\"#F(F(%\"cGF(F(F*!\"\"F-" }
}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 61 "sets the equation equal to zero \+
